        Since 2013, we've coached and consulted thousands of financial advisors, RIAs, and wirehouse teams, delivering next-level transformations.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 mb-16">
      <div class="cardRecipe p-8 animate-on-scroll" data-card-recipe="primary">
