            <div class="statRecipe">23 New Clients/Year</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="cardRecipe p-8 animate-on-scroll">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-normal text-stone-900 mb-4">Client Success Spotlight</h3>
        <blockquote class="text-lg italic text-stone-700 mb-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          "Select Advisors Institute transformed our practice. We went from $250 million to $1.5 billion AUM in just five years. Their strategic guidance and sales training were game-changers for our entire team."
